Module it.polimi.ingsw.triton.launcher
Package it.polimi.ingsw.triton.launcher.client

Class ServerMessageVisitor

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.triton.launcher.client.ServerMessageVisitor
public class ServerMessageVisitor extends Object
This visitor manages messages sent by the server to establish which view methods to call and to modify the client model.
